---
description: Apply when doing SEO, CRO, UX, or copy analysis
globs: ["**/*.html", "**/*.md", "**/*.tsx", "**/*.jsx"]
---

When analysing pages for marketing:
1. Check title tag, meta description, H1 alignment
2. Evaluate CTA clarity, placement, and value proposition
3. Review copy against audience pain points
4. Check page speed signals and Core Web Vitals if accessible
5. Identify missing schema markup
6. Prioritise findings: Critical → Important → Nice-to-have
Output must include: current state / issue / recommended fix / priority
